  "title": "Data Analyst",
  "description": "<p>CCS is looking for a highly motivated Data Analyst. This role is\ncritical in transforming data into actionable insights that drive business\ndecisions. The successful candidate will be responsible for reporting, trend analysis, and collaborating with stakeholders to deliver data-driven solutions.</p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Utilize Python for data processing, automation, and advanced analytics.</li><li>Develop and maintain reports and dashboards using Power BI.</li><li>Perform trend analysis and identify patterns to support strategic initiatives.</li><li>Present findings and recommendations to management in a clear, concise, and impactful manner.</li></ul><p>Required Skills & Qualifications</p><ul><li>Strong proficiency in Python for data manipulation and analysis.</li><li>Expertise in Power BI for visualization and reporting.</li><li>Solid understanding of trend analysis, statistical methods, and data modeling.</li><li>Excellent communication skills to convey complex data insights effectively.</li></ul>",
